<p><strong><em>Fey Ancestry.</em></strong> Aerisi has advantage on saving throws against being charmed, and magic canâ€™t put her to sleep.</p>

<p><strong><em>Howling Defeat.</em></strong> When Aerisi drops to 0 hit points, her body disappears in a howling whirlwind that disperses quickly and harmlessly. Anything she is wearing or carrying is left behind.</p>

<p><strong><em>Legendary Resistance (2/Day).</em></strong> If Aerisi fails a saving throw, she can choose to succeed instead.</p>

<p><strong><em>Spellcasting.</em></strong> Aerisi is a 12th-level spellcaster. Her spellcasting ability is Intelligence (spell save DC 14, +6 to hit with spell attacks). Aerisi has the following wizard spells prepared:</p>

